</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Kaczmarek" pageId="75" pageNumber="76" refString="Kaczmarek, L. &amp; Michalczyk, L. (2009 b) Two new species of Macrobiotidae, Macrobiotus szeptyckii (harmsworthi group) and Macrobiotus kazmierskii (hufelandi group) from Argentina. Acta Zoologica Cracoviensia, 52 B, 87 - 99. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.3409 / azc. 52 b _ 1 - 2.87 - 99" type="journal article" year="2009" yearSuffix="b">
